data.description: PRICE REDUCTION.  PRICE REDUCTION. This lovely family homes has 4 generous sized bedrooms, is close to Fairview Elementary and the Splash Park.  There are closets and storage galore throughout, and a partially finished attic space, with a door from a bedroom for easy access. There is a well maintained, large, manicured lawn with a rock pathway from the patio leading to a storage building with an oversized door and decked sitting area.  There is still plenty of room for relaxation, a trampoline or a playscape. Let's not forget the above ground pool, with it's raised decking for your outdoor furniture and for you to enjoy the seasons from summer evenings to crisp winter mornings. There are sturdy steps for easy entry and exit, a pump and filtration system help keep the pool crystal clear. There are an array of many colorful flowering perennials that will bloom from spring time through the fall.  The mature tree lends shade and tranquility to this very peaceful, private, backyard.
